# Week 2 - Object Detection using YOLO

## Objective
In this week, I learned how to use a pretrained YOLO model for object detection on images and multiple frames.

## Task 1: Virtual Environment Setup
- Created a virtual environment using venv
- Activated the environment before installing packages
## Task 2: Installing Ultralytics
- Installed ultralytics package inside the virtual environment
## Task 3: Object Detection on Image
- Used YOLO pretrained model to detect objects in an image 
## Additional Task: Object Detection on Multiple Images
- Used frames extracted in Week 1
- Applied YOLO detection on multiple images using Python script
- Saved annotated images in a separate folder

## Tools Used
- Python (venv)  
- Ultralytics YOLO  
- FFmpeg  
- GitHub  
